blockquote><br />\n<br />\n南記個春卷好正喎<br />\n三哥都有墨丸同皮蛋白肉<br />\n雲桂香就冇樣拎得出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n腩肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得大腸腩肉都唔錯<br />\n但係未去到招牌級數<br />\nbtw我幾鐘意佢個涼拌米線同過橋米線"},{"pid":"94670e254880cb5afda9e9bdcf8667d7d2631757","tid":424783,"uid":149485,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:49:19.000Z","msg":"魚米都第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  肯定最尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc729f79a3a2ba65f923f66a7b0953a660d75be6","tid":424783,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:57:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魚米都第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  肯定最尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪即係魚米家?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔係專做米線，但魚腐好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694b2dab14ee21701ec7f1130c6775a71f54134b","tid":424783,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魚米都第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  肯定最尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"e05026cc9442941953b011687f24d28849b07712","tid":424783,"uid":28651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e855f6b665450c4b6a085a452b046372753a509","tid":424783,"uid":148224,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.南記<br />\n2.魚米<br />\n3.雲桂香<br />\n4.譚仔三哥<br />\n5.米線陣<br />\n<br />\n排完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南記：平，味道中下<br />\n<br />\n魚米：初初食佢個魚湯都覺得ok, 而家行過舖門口聞到就魚湯味就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲桂香：小鍋米線味道正宗，最鍾意食佢個豬軟骨；不過越加越貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋出品水準極飄忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三哥：出品水準穩定，三酸好食，不過少餸選擇同偏貴（人均$50up）<br />\n<br />\n米線陣：食過一次，垃圾，不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da7b67d5d9adec497c3b0c6f2794f62bc7e69e7","tid":424783,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"點睇雲貴軒"},{"pid":"fc98417b6bebdfc7cebdec7f7912a312c6fdf533","tid":424783,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>魚米都第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  肯定最尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪即係魚米家?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔係專做米線，但魚腐好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔同 魚米家未食過<br />\n魚米=魚湯+米線 咁都唔專?"},{"pid":"98b8510b98e6ce01a23d29d5ddd16cd97559df55","tid":424783,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"覺得米線陣最好食但最貴"},{"pid":"25fd3dad44b1beabf075289811ac4a9727d840bc","tid":424783,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T10:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1.南記<br />\n2.魚米<br />\n3.雲桂香<br />\n4.譚仔三哥<br />\n5.米線陣<br />\n<br />\n排完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南記：平，味道中下<br />\n<br />\n魚米：初初食佢個魚湯都覺得ok, 而家行過舖門口聞到就魚湯味就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲桂香：小鍋米線味道正宗，最鍾意食佢個豬軟骨；不過越加越貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋出品水準極飄忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三哥：出品水準穩定，三酸好食，不過少餸選擇同偏貴（人均$50up）<br />\n<br />\n米線陣：食過一次，垃圾，不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解聞魚湯味會想嘔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雲桂香好飄忽，差嗰陣好差，特別係旺角嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb52990a46c61113fd7e98c9d0563fed7f81a24f","tid":424783,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1.南記<br />\n2.魚米<br />\n3.雲桂香<br />\n4.譚仔三哥<br />\n5.米線陣<br />\n<br />\n排完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南記：平，味道中下<br />\n<br />\n魚米：初初食佢個魚湯都覺得ok, 而家行過舖門口聞到就魚湯味就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲桂香：小鍋米線味道正宗，最鍾意食佢個豬軟骨；不過越加越貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋出品水準極飄忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三哥：出品水準穩定，三酸好食，不過少餸選擇同偏貴（人均$50up）<br />\n<br />\n米線陣：食過一次，垃圾，不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解聞魚湯味會想嘔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雲桂香好飄忽，差嗰陣好差，特別係旺角嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n魚米個魚湯好臭膠"},{"pid":"210