ormal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c9bd9105b1c51d8da3a29f906328576af0fa01","tid":424783,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雲桂香世界第一</blockquote><br />\n一滴香世界第一"},{"pid":"b2a73981e06a76df7ce7ee55dacb02463f2f318b","tid":424783,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T11:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺得米線陣最好食但最貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好貴 好多款野但冇乜特別<br />\n試過幾款湯 味道麻麻</blockquote><br />\n貴得黎好少下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而幾中意食佢既大汗雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 餸唔多 但湯好似有6款以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢小食可以出串魚蛋仲要唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw三哥土匪正啲"},{"pid":"58d4607c4aa700d845e8b3a1bfb748b654683c77","tid":424783,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"你地係直程唔食魚湯，<br />\n定係剩係唔鍾意魚米個湯？"},{"pid":"bd3177c578973e3862108fbb8c909c22a0b78191","tid":424783,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地係直程唔食魚湯，<br />\n定係剩係唔鍾意魚米個湯？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n魚湯米線以前都開得幾多<br />\n但連鎖應該係得魚米同魚米家"},{"pid":"df849baf565da58b0bf73754faa151e8a7d4c7d8","tid":424783,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"原來有間叫景霖，開咗5間<br />\n有冇巴絲食過?"},{"pid":"ff4056e46f62e497e56131554dc0b46ff481e01e","tid":424783,"uid":35445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T08:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1.南記<br />\n2.魚米<br />\n3.雲桂香<br />\n4.譚仔三哥<br />\n5.米線陣<br />\n<br />\n排完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南記：平，味道中下<br />\n<br />\n魚米：初初食佢個魚湯都覺得ok, 而家行過舖門口聞到就魚湯味就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲桂香：小鍋米線味道正宗，最鍾意食佢個豬軟骨；不過越加越貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋出品水準極飄忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三哥：出品水準穩定，三酸好食，不過少餸選擇同偏貴（人均$50up）<br />\n<br />\n米線陣：食過一次，垃圾，不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你食譚仔每次幾多個餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31425425f631757ec212a1c10a88776207e7545e","tid":424783,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1.南記<br />\n2.魚米<br />\n3.雲桂香<br />\n4.譚仔三哥<br />\n5.米線陣<br />\n<br />\n排完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南記：平，味道中下<br />\n<br />\n魚米：初初食佢個魚湯都覺得ok, 而家行過舖門口聞到就魚湯味就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲桂香：小鍋米線味道正宗，最鍾意食佢個豬軟骨；不過越加越貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋出品水準極飄忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三哥：出品水準穩定，三酸好食，不過少餸選擇同偏貴（人均$50up）<br />\n<br />\n米線陣：食過一次，垃圾，不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你食譚仔每次幾多個餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我食開2-3餸<br />\n同意少餸選擇"},{"pid":"c9cebb3f9761ba3c3566e94598f746d6a286b25c","tid":424783,"uid":36911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"南記D米線咁多間連所最好食"},{"pid":"064433f5a0ef706c00b0ae2f04d84cd57ea0e2e3","tid":424783,"ui